===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''chloroform'''
# {{chemistry}} a [[halogenated]] [[hydrocarbon]], [[trichloromethane]], CHCl<sub>3</sub>; it is a volatile, sweet-smelling liquid, used extensively as a [[solvent]] and formerly as an [[anesthetic]]

===Transitive verb===
